then users of the API would essentially need to provide an API key

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:52.000
in order to leverage this API,

00:15:52.000 --> 00:15:55.000
and that API key, you can actually log into Connect,

00:15:55.000 --> 00:16:02.000
click on your name, and generate those keys right over here.

