And we're going to feed in two parameters,

00:17:01.000 --> 00:17:03.000
which are essentially going to extract data

00:17:03.000 --> 00:17:06.000
where the letters column is equal to F, G, or R.

00:17:06.000 --> 00:17:10.000
So let's go ahead and run this.

