00:18:16.000 --> 00:18:19.000
So here in the top left corner, this is the Shiny application.

00:18:19.000 --> 00:18:21.000
It's nothing but R code,

00:18:21.000 --> 00:18:24.000
which is used to create interactive web applications.

00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:27.000
So we're going to use the Shiny package for this,

00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:31.000
but also note that we're using this JSON Lite and HTTR package

00:18:31.000 --> 00:18:33.000
to interact with our API.

00:18:33.000 --> 00:18:37.000
So I'm going to scroll down here to the server function

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:39.000
