00:18:39.000 --> 00:18:43.000
which is going to be important for pinging our API.

00:18:43.000 --> 00:18:46.000
So this first bit of code right here,

00:18:46.000 --> 00:18:49.000
this is where we actually ping that API.

00:18:49.000 --> 00:18:52.000
So we feed it that API URL, which I saved as a variable,

00:18:52.000 --> 00:18:57.000
and we can provide some query parameters to that API.

00:18:57.000 --> 00:18:59.000
We then take that response.

00:18:59.000 --> 00:19:01.000
All right, we gather it here,

00:19:01.000 --> 00:19:04.000
and then we convert that JSON response into a data frame,

00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:07.000
which will eventually be converted over to a TIBL.

00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:11.000
We save that as a response data, which gets fed into a ggplot.

